(24, 'cursos_pgc', '<div id=\"titulo\" class=\"page-title\" data-aos=\"fade\">\r\n<div class=\"heading\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-center text-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n<h1>Cursos</h1>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Na <strong>TutorMatch</strong>, oferecemos uma ampla gama de cursos online, desenvolvidos para atender &agrave;s suas necessidades de aprendizado, seja voc&ecirc; iniciante ou profissional. Nossos cursos s&atilde;o elaborados por especialistas de diversas &aacute;reas, com conte&uacute;do atualizado e material de qualidade, para garantir que voc&ecirc; aprenda de forma eficaz e pr&aacute;tica. Se voc&ecirc; busca aprimorar suas habilidades, conquistar novos conhecimentos ou at&eacute; mesmo mudar de &aacute;rea, a <strong>TutorMatch</strong> &eacute; o lugar certo para voc&ecirc;. Com a flexibilidade do ensino online, voc&ecirc; pode aprender no seu pr&oacute;prio ritmo, de qualquer lugar!</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<nav class=\"breadcrumbs\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://localhost:3030/index.html\">Home</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"current\">Cursos</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</nav></div>'),
(25, 'cursos_resto', '<section id=\"coursese\" class=\"courses section\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-delay=\"100\">\r\n<div class=\"course-item\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://localhost:3030/assets/img/dinamicas/DS.jpg\" alt=\"...\" width=\"730\" height=\"487\">\r\n<div class=\"course-content\">\r\n<div class=\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3\">\r\n<p class=\"category\">Desenvolvimento de Sistemas</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">R$ 599,00</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://localhost:3030/course-details.html\">Design de site</a></h3>\r\n<p class=\"description\">Aprenda a criar e gerenciar sistemas modernos, desde fundamentos de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o at&eacute; tecnologias avan&ccedil;adas como web e mobile. Ideal para quem busca uma carreira na &aacute;rea de tecnologia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"trainer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"trainer-profile d-flex align-items-center\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://localhost:3030/assets/img/trainers/trainer-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"> <a class=\"trainer-link\">Antonio</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"trainer-rank d-flex align-items-center\">&nbsp;50 &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;65</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End Course Item-->\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch mt-4 mt-md-0\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-delay=\"200\">\r\n<div class=\"course-item\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://localhost:3030/assets/img/dinamicas/ADM.jpg\" alt=\"...\" width=\"597\" height=\"398\">\r\n<div class=\"course-content\">\r\n<div class=\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3\">\r\n<p class=\"category\">Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">R$399,00</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://localhost:3030/index.html\"><strong>Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o</strong></a></h3>\r\n<p class=\"description\">Domine os principais conceitos de gest&atilde;o, finan&ccedil;as e lideran&ccedil;a com este curso voltado para futuros gestores e empreendedores. Perfeito para alavancar sua carreira no mundo dos neg&oacute;cios.</p>\r\n<div class=\"trainer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"trainer-profile d-flex align-items-center\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://localhost:3030/assets/img/trainers/trainer-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"> <a class=\"trainer-link\">Lana</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"trainer-rank d-flex align-items-center\">&nbsp;35 &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;42</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End Course Item-->\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch mt-4 mt-lg-0\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-delay=\"300\">\r\n<div class=\"course-item\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"https://www.vocepodefalaringles.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bandeira-dos-estados-unidos-da-america_1401-253.jpg\" alt=\"...\" width=\"606\" height=\"404\">\r\n<div class=\"course-content\">\r\n<div class=\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3\">\r\n<p class=\"category\">Ingl&ecirc;s</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">R$299,00</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://localhost:3030/index.html\">Ingl&ecirc;s</a></h3>\r\n<p class=\"description\">Adquira flu&ecirc;ncia no ingl&ecirc;s com aulas din&acirc;micas focadas em conversa&ccedil;&atilde;o, gram&aacute;tica e vocabul&aacute;rio. Perfeito para viagens, trabalho ou certifica&ccedil;&otilde;es internacionais podendo at&eacute; mesmo obter interc&acirc;mbios gratuitos.</p>\r\n<div class=\"trainer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"trainer-profile d-flex align-items-center\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"http://localhost:3030/assets/img/trainers/trainer-3-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"> <a class=\"trainer-link\">Brandon</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"trainer-rank d-flex align-items-center\">&nbsp;20 &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;85</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End Course Item--></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>');
